data.description: Say hello to your dream home in the Parks! This 4-bed, 3-bath gem is your ticket to easy, comfortable living. Inside, a modern farmhouse kitchen straight out of Pinterest: white cabinets, granite, large farmhouse sink, shiny appliances and a walk in pantry. Fresh paint and new carpet gives brand-new allure. The backyard is like your own personal paradise with lush artificial turf & stylish pavers. Perfect for grilling under the AZ stars! The Queen Creek Olive Mill & Schnepf Farms are practically in your backyard too! Need to hit the road? Meridian Rd links you to the 24 and 202 Freeway seamlessly. This isn't just a home; it's your comfy, stylish escape, inside and out. Plus, it's rare for this floor plan to become available. Snag it while you can! Your dream life starts here!
